name: UNICURSAL HEXAGRAM - GIF
description:
The unicursal hexagram is a six pointed star that can be drawn unicursally. It is regularly depicted in an interlaced form, with its lines passing over and under one another - creating a knot. This specific design has all these attributes and flashes in colour. It is an ideal GIF for anyone interested in mysticism, the occult, esoteric studies or science. AS ABOVE, SO BELOW.

*Made using mathematical equations.
